reviews.review_text: Don't ease me in I created an account here just to comment on how great this source is. This show has always been a favorite of mine so when I stumbled upon this source, I was extremely impressed. Thanks to the heads that worked together to provide us with another source to add to our collections. I haven't listened to all the available sources on the Archive to make a comparison, so you'll have to take my word for it :-) A+
